{
  "stem": "26576.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a lot of people-- I think that, from a two and a half thousand-- they were saying two and a half thousand that we started, that came-- that when we came, only a few hundred survived.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a very rough time, and again, the same situation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Even the-- the bread that we got, that wasn't hardly enough to live on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, you couldn't live on that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- so I remember the first winter, we-- my brother and myself would go to where some fields-- that there were some peasants not far away-- and we would just steal potatoes.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, we would-- we would-- under the snow, with our bare hands, [INAUDIBLE] would steal potatoes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this is how-- and this-- the months of winter, I remember having potatoes, and we're very lucky.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My mother would make potatoes in all different shapes and variation, you know, because this is the only food that one could get there the way we got it, and we were scared to if they would catch us.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know what would have happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so this part was the part where we were, which was called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That camp there was a very-- as I said, a few hundred people survived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Mostly people that had families were better off in a way because, somehow, you combined the bread ration and that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But there was a lot of single people, and single people were dying out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Terrible.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I myself-- I became ill.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I got diphtheria after a few months, and they put me-- there was no hospitals, but there was quite, where my school was, there was also-- they called it an [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This was a room where there was a nurse.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
